[
    {
        "text": "Once upon a time, there lived a sage called Mrikandu with his wife Marudavati.",
        "start": 24.8,
        "duration": 7.32
    },
    {
        "text": "They were childless for a long time.",
        "start": 37.76,
        "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
        "text": "Mrikandu performed intense tapas in order to please Lord Shiva.",
        "start": 40.66,
        "duration": 5.02
    },
    {
        "text": "Lord Shiva, in all his splendor",
        "start": 47.9,
        "duration": 2.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Appeared before him.",
        "start": 50.94,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "I am pleased by your devotion.",
        "start": 52.84,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Ask from me any boon you desire.",
        "start": 55.2,
        "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh Lord. I am childless.",
        "start": 57.68,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Grant me a son.",
        "start": 60.3,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you desire to have a virtuous, wise and pious son,",
        "start": 62.08,
        "duration": 3.5
    },
    {
        "text": "who will live up to only sixteen years?",
        "start": 65.72,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "or a dull- witted, evil-natured son who will live long?",
        "start": 68.04,
        "duration": 4.68
    },
    {
        "text": "Grant me the Child who is intelligent",
        "start": 74.04,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "But short life than one who is not",
        "start": 76.61,
        "duration": 3.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Intelligent enough to make use of him for the right purpose.",
        "start": 80.04,
        "duration": 3.46
    },
    {
        "text": "As you wish Mrikandu.",
        "start": 84.36,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "You shall have him.",
        "start": 86.16,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "An accomplished sage early in his childhood",
        "start": 104.04,
        "duration": 3.02
    },
    {
        "text": "He was especially",
        "start": 107.98,
        "duration": 1.34
    },
    {
        "text": "Devoted to Shiva.",
        "start": 109.56,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "His pleasing ways endeared him to his teachers.",
        "start": 111.12,
        "duration": 3.86
    },
    {
        "text": "The boy was liked by one and all.",
        "start": 115.0,
        "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
        "text": "He was thus spending his days very happily.",
        "start": 126.18,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "Delighting everyone by his charming looks and",
        "start": 129.52,
        "duration": 3.14
    },
    {
        "text": "pleasant behavior.",
        "start": 132.8,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Sixteenth year was fast approaching.",
        "start": 156.12,
        "duration": 2.574
    },
    {
        "text": "Mrikandu and his wife started becoming",
        "start": 158.7,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "Apprehensive.",
        "start": 161.52,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "Fearing that they would soon lose the son whom they loved so much.",
        "start": 162.96,
        "duration": 5.06
    },
    {
        "text": "Father..",
        "start": 170.94,
        "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Why do you look so sad?",
        "start": 172.02,
        "duration": 1.235
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh,My son",
        "start": 173.26,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "According to Lord Shiva's boon,",
        "start": 174.84,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "You are destined to live only for sixteen years",
        "start": 177.28,
        "duration": 3.8
    },
    {
        "text": "How can we withstand this?",
        "start": 181.98,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "We are helpless",
        "start": 184.4,
        "duration": 1.1
    },
    {
        "text": "and do not know what to do.",
        "start": 185.96,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Father..",
        "start": 188.28,
        "duration": 0.86
    },
    {
        "text": "You have taught me the Vedas, the Puranas and the Shashtras.",
        "start": 189.14,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "You have taught me that,",
        "start": 193.22,
        "duration": 1.22
    },
    {
        "text": "the Lord,",
        "start": 194.62,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Always listens to the sincere prayers of his devotees.",
        "start": 195.12,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "It is Lord Shiva, who has decreed",
        "start": 199.04,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "that I should live for sixteen years.",
        "start": 201.32,
        "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
        "text": "I Shall pray to him and ask him to extend my lifespan.",
        "start": 204.32,
        "duration": 3.86
    },
    {
        "text": "He will surely answer to my sincere prayers.",
        "start": 208.7,
        "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
        "text": "The parents blessed him heartily and sent him for penance.",
        "start": 215.38,
        "duration": 4.46
    },
    {
        "text": "Markandeya walked through a dense forest",
        "start": 223.76,
        "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
        "text": "and reached the river banks.",
        "start": 226.66,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "There, He made a shivalingam with sand",
        "start": 256.3,
        "duration": 3.58
    },
    {
        "text": "and started performing",
        "start": 260.1,
        "duration": 1.18
    },
    {
        "text": "severe penance.",
        "start": 261.38,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "He was soon engrossed in deep meditation",
        "start": 263.2,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "Days and nights passed.",
        "start": 276.48,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "In Yamaloka,",
        "start": 296.8,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Yama ordered his servants to collect Markandeya's soul.",
        "start": 298.0,
        "duration": 3.98
    },
    {
        "text": "On reaching Markandeya's place,",
        "start": 310.7,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "they saw Markandeya meditating before the Shivalingam.",
        "start": 313.14,
        "duration": 3.38
    },
    {
        "text": "Markandeya was so deep in meditation",
        "start": 344.38,
        "duration": 2.68
    },
    {
        "text": "That a strange fierce light emerged from him.",
        "start": 347.36,
        "duration": 3.7
    },
    {
        "text": "The light from him was burning so brightly,",
        "start": 352.0,
        "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
        "text": "that the servants of yama could not get close to him.",
        "start": 355.16,
        "duration": 3.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Why can't we reach him?",
        "start": 364.88,
        "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
        "text": "If we go empty hand, our master will punish us.",
        "start": 366.72,
        "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
        "text": "What should we do now?",
        "start": 370.38,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "I guess he's no ordinary boy.",
        "start": 372.58,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Look over there.",
        "start": 374.66,
        "duration": 0.52
    },
    {
        "text": "That Shivalingam is protecting him from us.",
        "start": 375.5,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Facing failure for the first time,",
        "start": 381.9,
        "duration": 2.404
    },
    {
        "text": "the servants returned to their master.",
        "start": 384.304,
        "duration": 2.616
    },
    {
        "text": "Master, we could not approach him.",
        "start": 390.88,
        "duration": 2.38
    },
    {
        "text": "There was something coming from him.",
        "start": 393.72,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "Something very bright,",
        "start": 396.04,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "that is protecting the boy.",
        "start": 397.86,
        "duration": 2.051
    },
    {
        "text": "We are very sorry for our failure.",
        "start": 399.92,
        "duration": 2.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Ah! Stupids.",
        "start": 402.7,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "Can't you even take the soul from a small boy?",
        "start": 404.5,
        "duration": 3.7
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, I will take care of this myself.",
        "start": 408.74,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Saying so,",
        "start": 412.84,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "Yama then picked up his noose and sat on his buffalo.",
        "start": 414.28,
        "duration": 4.56
    },
    {
        "text": "And disappeared from his place.",
        "start": 418.94,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "In Markandeya's place,",
        "start": 424.18,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Yama at once realized that the boy was pure and had lived a good life.",
        "start": 426.42,
        "duration": 5.8
    },
    {
        "text": "As Markandeya was a noble child,",
        "start": 435.72,
        "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
        "text": "so Yama made himself visible.",
        "start": 438.22,
        "duration": 2.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Markandeya,",
        "start": 444.64,
        "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Your time on earth is up.",
        "start": 446.12,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "I will not go with you.",
        "start": 458.32,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "My Lord will protect me.",
        "start": 460.42,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "Your time on earth is up.",
        "start": 462.06,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "I have come to take you.",
        "start": 464.8,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "Markandeya shook his head and hugged the Shivalinga tightly.",
        "start": 468.5,
        "duration": 5.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Realizing that he had no choice,",
        "start": 474.88,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Yama threw his noose around Markandeya's neck",
        "start": 477.84,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "to pull out his soul.",
        "start": 481.7,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Unfortunately Yama's noose fell around both Markandeya's neck and the Shivalinga.",
        "start": 483.64,
        "duration": 7.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh Lord,",
        "start": 505.54,
        "duration": 0.78
    },
    {
        "text": "save me.",
        "start": 506.32,
        "duration": 0.84
    },
    {
        "text": "To his surprise",
        "start": 514.0,
        "duration": 1.14
    },
    {
        "text": "He felt the linga move with his closed eyes.",
        "start": 515.44,
        "duration": 3.8
    },
    {
        "text": "He opened his eyes with astonishment.",
        "start": 519.24,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "Markandeya was thrilled to see the three-eyed Lord before him.",
        "start": 522.88,
        "duration": 4.98
    },
    {
        "text": "How dare you disturb him?",
        "start": 536.54,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "My Lord..",
        "start": 540.96,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "His time on Earth is up.",
        "start": 542.24,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "I have come.",
        "start": 544.6,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "He will live forever",
        "start": 545.62,
        "duration": 1.58
    },
    {
        "text": "How dare you?",
        "start": 547.46,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "Every line of Shiva's face was fierce with anger.",
        "start": 549.12,
        "duration": 3.94
    },
    {
        "text": "Shiva picked up his trident",
        "start": 571.9,
        "duration": 2.121
    },
    {
        "text": "and pierced Yama.",
        "start": 574.021,
        "duration": 1.659
    },
    {
        "text": "Yama caught the weapon straight in his chest.",
        "start": 575.68,
        "duration": 3.693
    },
    {
        "text": "He fell down dead.",
        "start": 579.373,
        "duration": 1.067
    },
    {
        "text": "Immediately Lord Indra and the other Devas appeared before Lord Shiva.",
        "start": 581.3,
        "duration": 5.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Lord Shiva..",
        "start": 588.1,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "We need to have a Lord of the Dead",
        "start": 589.66,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Without death,",
        "start": 591.98,
        "duration": 1.22
    },
    {
        "text": "there would be no balance on earth.",
        "start": 593.2,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Please Lord..",
        "start": 595.28,
        "duration": 0.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Give Yama his life back.",
        "start": 596.18,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "So that the balance of life can be restored.",
        "start": 597.56,
        "duration": 2.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes..",
        "start": 600.34,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes..",
        "start": 601.2,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Alright.",
        "start": 602.16,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Yama shall have his life back if",
        "start": 602.96,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "And only if Markandeya is spared.",
        "start": 605.44,
        "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
        "text": "Markandeya will live forever.",
        "start": 608.14,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "He will be the one who has conquered death.",
        "start": 610.58,
        "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
        "text": "At once Yama opened his eyes,",
        "start": 615.7,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "as the wound in his chest healed.",
        "start": 618.9,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Yama looked at Lord Shiva and said,",
        "start": 621.78,
        "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh Lord!",
        "start": 625.22,
        "duration": 0.68
    },
    {
        "text": "Forgive my mistake.",
        "start": 626.06,
        "duration": 1.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Now I can understand the power of true devotion to you.",
        "start": 628.28,
        "duration": 4.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Your mistakes are forgiven.",
        "start": 633.36,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "Go to your heavenly abode and continue your duty.",
        "start": 635.92,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Yama and the other devas returned to their heavenly abode.",
        "start": 639.22,
        "duration": 4.36
    },
    {
        "text": "Markandeya,",
        "start": 646.1,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "then fell at the feet of the Lord Shiva and said,",
        "start": 647.3,
        "duration": 3.66
    },
    {
        "text": "Lord, I want nothing more.",
        "start": 651.88,
        "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
        "text": "I have seen you.",
        "start": 655.34,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Go back to your parents, Markandeya.",
        "start": 657.1,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "Look after them for their life.",
        "start": 659.2,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "After that,",
        "start": 661.64,
        "duration": 0.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Roam the Earth and be peaceful doing whatever you wish.",
        "start": 662.94,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "You have my blessings.",
        "start": 666.78,
        "duration": 1.96
    }
]